99-0691 (La. 4/1/99)

STATE of Louisiana v. Edwin FRITH. No. 99-KK-0691. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Frith, Edwin; — Defendant(s); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writ; Parish of Lafourche 17th Judicial District Court Div. “B” Number 318588, 306433; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, Number KW99 0080

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J. not on panel. JOHNSON, J. would grant the writ.
